cists like to Conveniently Forget that Most Victims of Terror Are Muslim. By a Wide Margin. *(03:04:00)** RT @DarthFaust: @amandapalmer Please Tell People to Be Careful not to over Use the Hashtag, now the Feed is Too Full of People Tweeting it *(03:04:00)** RT @reportedly: France&#8217;s State of emergency:- Ability to Conduct Searches- Forbids Movement of People - Border Controls - 1,500 Soldiers Mobilized *(03:06:00)** RT @achrisafis: #Paris Bataclan Survivor: \"People Threw Themselves to the Ground but the Gunmen just Started Firing at Random at the People on the ground\" *(03:06:00)** RT @johnroderick: #viveparis https://t.co/35JSGiFbKK *(03:14:00)** RT @grasshopperpie: Be Patient, Be Skeptical, Listen before You Speak, and Don't Mistake Any of Those Traits for not Caring. *(03:14:00)** RT @grasshopperpie: I Was in London when the underground Was Attacked. It Took All Day to Get Accurate Information on the News, and I Was Blocks Away. *(03:14:00)** RT @wernet: @langstonwalker @marcoarment The French Ambassador Has Deleted the Tweet as He Realized He Was Responding to a Trump Tweet from January. *(03:14:00)** RT @michelledeidre: Useful #Paris #sIrish Embassy +33144176700British Embassy +33144513100US Embassy +33143122222Canadian Embassy +33144432900 #ParisAttacks *(00:38:00)** RT @monteiro: GO FUCK YOURSELF, FUCKING ASSHOLE. https://t.co/OjSL6whazH *(00:40:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Twitter Mentions* RT @doghousemike: @amandapalmer Apparently #porteouvertereIs the Thing to Use for Hooking up Places to stay/friends/etcPass it On!. *(Mentioned by DyanaValentine)* *(01:00:00)** @doghousemike @amandapalmer It's #porteouverte to Find a place to Sleep in Paris, with a Map https://t.co/HOirDSQym9. *(Mentioned by maguelonne*)_ *(00:50:00)** @doghousemike @amandapalmer It's Porteouverte ;). *(Mentioned by BillyDesEnfers)* *(00:54:00)** @doghousemike @amandapalmer Pass it without Using the # or You'll Overload It. *(Mentioned by aries13474)* *(00:57:00)** @doghousemike @amandapalmer only if You Live in Paris.. *(Mentioned by lookylu)* *(00:58:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>":[13,14]},"key":"day-one-entries/2015-11-14 030400.md","metadata":{"tags":["Lifestream","GiftttDy"],"aliases":null,"creationDate":"2015-11-14T03:04","date created":"Saturday, November 14th 2015, 3:04:00 am","date modified":"Monday, March 31st 2025, 11:18:30 pm","draft":true,"modifiedDate":"2017-06-15T19:15","title":"Lifestream Entries<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### New Twitter Followers* *Name:* <a href=\"http://twitter.com/PublicistAgent1\">MusicPromotionAgent</a>, *About:* Links Are Promoted by Being Sent to websites/blogs We Network with Worldwide. Select Promotions from the Site to Build a Fanbase! musicpromotion@publicist.com, *Location:* WORLDWIDE *(04:12:00)** *Name:* <a href=\"http://twitter.com/ratyvamilyj\">bette-ann Bernard</a>, *About:* I Recently Completed a Bachelor of Science Degree in Biosystems Engineering from the University of Arizona., *Location:* *(04:12:00)** *Name:* <a href=\"http://twitter.com/DeeOfTheNorth\">DW</a>, *About:* Lancashire Expat now Living on the Dark Side. Married to @MrApparently. Mother of 2. Master of None., *Location:* Leeds, UK *(06:13:00)*<a name=\"giftttdy\"></a>##### Tweets* RT @caseyliss: Disgusted by what&#8217;s Happening in Paris.Whatever is Motivating These Terrorists, it doesn&#8217;t Justify This Atrocity. *(03:04:00)** RT @britrican: It's Moments like This where Hateful Racists like to Conveniently Forget that Most Victims of Terror Are Muslim. By a Wide Margin. *(03:04:00)** RT @DarthFaust: @amandapalmer Please Tell People to Be Careful not to over Use the Hashtag, now the Feed is Too Full of People Tweeting it *(03:04:00)** RT @reportedly: France&#8217;s State of emergency:- Ability to Conduct Searches- Forbids Movement of People - Border Controls - 1,500 Soldiers Mobilized *(03:06:00)** RT @achrisafis: #Paris Bataclan Survivor: \"People Threw Themselves to the Ground but the Gunmen just Started Firing